full_description: The Hessian Center for Artificial Intelligence is an association of 13 Hessian universities and pursues the goal of conducting cutting-edge research with concrete practical relevance. As a research and innovation center, hessian.AI promotes the transfer of results to business and society through the training of AI talent, the promotion of start-ups and cooperation with companies.
